Then I would structure the document roughly like this:

# 1. Product Context

* Voice-first dental clinic operating system.
* Reception → Doctor → Reception workflow.
* AI structures information; it does not make clinical decisions.
* Treatment Plans are the primary business entity.
* Appointments are children of Treatment Plans.
* Authorization is clinic-scoped.

---

# 2. High-Level Architecture

```text
Frontend

↓

Middleware

↓

Validation

↓

Controllers

↓

Transaction Services

↓

AI Service

↓

Repositories

↓

Supabase
```

Controllers never access Supabase directly.

---

